  "text": "Remark 10. In model [CITATION_1] , the given satisfactory level is used to determine an -cut for a fuzzy number. For a fuzzy number\u0303with a concave membership function, its -cut\u0129 s an interval, denoted by\u0303\u00b1 . By decomposition theorem, we know\u0303=",
